org.apache.cassandra.index.sasi.utils.trie

Enum Cursor.Decision

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Cursor.Decision>
      • org.apache.cassandra.index.sasi.utils.trie.Cursor.Decision
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Cursor.Decision>
    Enclosing interface:
    Cursor<K,V>

    public static enum Cursor.Decision
extends java.lang.Enum<Cursor.Decision>
    The Cursor.Decision tells the Cursor what to do on each step while traversing the Trie. NOTE: Not all operations that work with a Cursor support all Cursor.Decision types

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      CONTINUE
      Continue with the traverse operation
      EXIT
      Exit the traverse operation
      REMOVE
      Remove the previously returned element from the Trie and continue
      REMOVE_AND_EXIT
      Remove the previously returned element from the Trie and exit from the traverse operation
